352    private static final String TAG = "Messages";
353
354    public static Map<Pair<Characteristic, Integer>, Class<? extends Message>> OPCODES = new HashMap<>();
355    public static Map<Integer, Messages> REQUESTS = new HashMap<>();
356    public static Map<Integer, Messages> RESPONSES = new HashMap<>();
357
358    static {
359        for (Messages m : Messages.values()) {
360            OPCODES.put(Pair.of(m.requestProps().characteristic(), m.requestOpCode), m.requestClass);
361            REQUESTS.put(m.requestOpCode, m);
362
363            OPCODES.put(Pair.of(m.responseProps().characteristic(), m.responseOpCode), m.responseClass);
364            RESPONSES.put(m.responseOpCode, m);
365
366            Validate.isTrue(m.requestProps().minApi().equals(m.responseProps().minApi()), "the minApi should match for " + m);
367        }
368
369        for (Characteristic c : Characteristic.values()) {
370            int errorOpcode = new ErrorResponse().opCode();
371            if (!OPCODES.containsKey(Pair.of(c, errorOpcode))) {
372                OPCODES.put(Pair.of(c, errorOpcode), ErrorResponse.class);
373            }
374        }
375    }
376
377    public static Message parse(byte[] data, int opCode, Characteristic characteristic) {
378        try {
379            Class<? extends Message> clazz = OPCODES.get(Pair.of(characteristic, opCode));
380            if (clazz == null) {
381                L.w(TAG, "Unable to find message for opCode: " + opCode +" for " + characteristic + " with data: " + Hex.encodeHexString(data));
382                return null;
383            }
384            Message msg = clazz.newInstance();
385            msg.parse(data);
386            return msg;
387        } catch (Exception e) {
388            L.w(TAG, "Unable to invoke parse of data: " + Hex.encodeHexString(data) + " opCode: " + opCode + " " + characteristic, e);
389            e.printStackTrace();
390            return null;
391        }
392    }
393
394    public static Set<Characteristic> findPossibleCharacteristicsForOpcode(int opCode) {
395        Set<Characteristic> items = new HashSet<>();
396        for (Pair<Characteristic, Integer> entry : OPCODES.keySet()) {
397            if (entry.getRight().equals(opCode)) {
398                items.add(entry.getLeft());
399            }
400        }
401
402        return items;
403    }
404
405    public static Set<Class<? extends Message>> findPossibleMessagesForCharacteristic(Characteristic characteristic) {
406        Set<Class<? extends Message>> items = new HashSet<>();
407        for (Map.Entry<Pair<Characteristic, Integer>, Class<? extends Message>> entry : OPCODES.entrySet()) {
408            if (entry.getKey().getLeft().equals(characteristic)) {
409                items.add(entry.getValue());
410            }
411        }
412
413        return items;
414    }
415
416    public static Class<? extends Message> fromOpcode(int opCode, Characteristic characteristic) {
417        return OPCODES.get(Pair.of(characteristic, opCode));
418    }
419
420    private final int requestOpCode;
421    private final Class<? extends Message> requestClass;
422    private final int responseOpCode;
423    private final Class<? extends Message> responseClass;
424    Messages(Class<? extends Message> requestClass, Class<? extends Message> responseClass) {
425        this.requestClass = requestClass;
426        this.requestOpCode = requestProps().opCode();
427        this.responseClass = responseClass;
428        this.responseOpCode = responseProps().opCode();
429    }
430
431    public int requestOpCode() {
432        return requestOpCode;
433    }
434    public Class<? extends Message> requestClass() {
435        return requestClass;
436    }
437    public MessageProps requestProps() {
438        return requestClass.getAnnotation(MessageProps.class);
439    }
440
441    public int responseOpCode() {
442        return responseOpCode;
443    }
444    public Class<? extends Message> responseClass() {
445        return responseClass;
446    }
447    public MessageProps responseProps() {
448        return responseClass.getAnnotation(MessageProps.class);
449    }
450
451    public Message request() {
452        try {
453            return requestClass.newInstance();
454        } catch (IllegalAccessException | InstantiationException | ClassCastException e) {
455            e.printStackTrace();
456            return null;
457        }
458    }
459    public Message response() {
460        try {
461            return responseClass.newInstance();
462        } catch (IllegalAccessException | InstantiationException | ClassCastException e) {
463            e.printStackTrace();
464            return null;
465        }
466    }
